{{Top|leg}}
A '''gravity bomb''' was a slow torpedo that was designed to attack larger ships. The explosion from the weapon would generate intense gravity waves designed to shake targets to pieces by disrupting the local gravitic fields. The weapons were used by the forces of [[Cronal]] at the [[Battle of Mindor]], by the [[Yevetha]], and by the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] at the [[Battle of Caamas]].

At the [[Battle of Mindor]], a single gravity bomb detonating nearby was sufficient to instantly destroy the ''[[Justice (MC80 Star Cruiser)|Justice]],'' an MC80 Liberty-type Star Cruiser<ref name="Shadows of Mindor">''[[Luke Skywalker and the Shadows of Mindor]]''</ref>.

